public abstract class CompletionPlugin
extends ServiceUserPlugin

This plugin gathers and integrates completion information from agents in a society to determin the "completion" of the current tasks. In most agents, it gathers the information and forwards the completion status of the agent to another agent. This process continues through a hierarchy of such plugins until the plugin at the root of the tree is reached. When the root determines that completion has been acheived (or is never going to be achieved), it advances the clock with the expectation that the advancement will engender additional activity and waits for the completion of that work.
